data.text:
Natalia (given name)

Natalia is a female given name. It is the Latin form of Natalie used also in Italian, Spanish and Polish.[1] Other spellings include Natália (Portuguese, Slovak and Hungarian) Nathália (Brazilian Portuguese), Natalya (Russian), Nataliya (Ukrainian), Natalija (Croatian, Latvian, Serbian, Slovene and Macedonian).[2]
